00:06:44.400 --> 00:06:46.680
Like, where are the relationship between the different packages?

00:06:46.680 --> 00:06:49.380
All the graph of the different dependencies?

00:06:49.420 --> 00:06:52.240
All these things are extremely important.

00:06:52.240 --> 00:06:58.340
So Daniel sent to BlueSky these posts on January 23

