00:11:09.480 --> 00:11:12.490
We have a pragmatic path to a more open future, like

00:11:12.490 --> 00:11:14.580
, we protect our trust network.

00:11:14.580 --> 00:11:16.510
We don't open everything directly.

00:11:16.640 --> 00:11:21.090
