00:11:37.740 --> 00:11:39.270
We are rooting for Tangle.

00:11:39.340 --> 00:11:40.770
We are rooting for Rumi.

00:11:40.800 --> 00:11:42.730
We are rooting for everything that you are building.

00:11:42.860 --> 00:11:46.260
And when things are ready, we are going to be mig

00:11:46.390 --> 00:11:47.570
rating there.

00:11:47.640 --> 00:11:52.080
And when we work in community, we are by humans and

00:11:52.090 --> 00:11:53.420
for humans.

00:11:53.420 --> 00:11:57.140
We-- our collaboration tools are community infrastructure.

00:11:57.140 --> 00:11:59.050
We, like, try to mix the-- and go to

00:11:59.200 --> 00:12:00.800
